- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also likely as the paper involves combinatorial analysis of palindromic decompositions of infinite words.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper deals with the computation of a function on an infinite word, which can be seen as a form of information processing.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves the study of a specific function on infinite words, which can be seen as a computational problem.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also less likely but possible as the paper involves the study of the complexity of computing a specific function on infinite words.
